snippet.title: Showcase: Alien Planet
snippet.description:
A first glimpse at a planet in Hyperventila. These strange glowing plants are a great way of demonstrating the real-time lighting in the game.

Join us and follow Hyperventila on social media!

Discord: https://discord.gg/ZX6YDWS

Twitter: https://twitter.com/HyperventilaDev

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hyperventila

Website: https://www.hyperventila.com

And of course if you like you can support development on Patreon: 

https://www.patreon.com/hyperventila


Note: Hyperventila is a game currently in development, this footage is not necessarily representative of the final game.
